<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4358762>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 8. Positions of a male of Stenobothrus miramae during the element 3 of courtship. (A) The male hits a female several times with his head; (B) the male slowly raises both hind femora and keeps them over head." ;
